title: William and Cnut: a tale of two conquerors
itunes:title: William and Cnut: a tale of two conquerors
itunes:subtitle: Emily Ward explains how the Danish conquest of England in 1016 is crucial to our understanding of what happened 50 years later. Historyextra.com/podcast
description:
Historian Emily Ward, co-editor of a new book on the conquests of 1016 and 1066, explains how the earlier Danish invasion of England is crucial to our understanding of what happened 50 years later. Historyextra.com/podcast
